{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# Sentinel Ingestion Cost Analysis\n---\nThis workbook provides visibility into Microsoft Sentinel ingestion costs. It identifies which tables are configured for **Analytics** vs **Auxiliary (Data Lake)** retention plans and calculates estimated costs based on ingestion volume.\n\n> Cross-reference the **Table Retention Plans** section with the **Ingestion by Table** section to determine actual cost per table based on its configured plan."
      },
      "name": "title"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimeRange",
            "label": "Time Range",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                { "durationMs": 86400000 },
                { "durationMs": 259200000 },
                { "durationMs": 604800000 },
                { "durationMs": 1209600000 },
                { "durationMs": 2592000000 },
                { "durationMs": 5184000000 },
                { "durationMs": 7776000000 }
              ],
              "allowCustom": true
            },
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 2592000000
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-bcde-f12345678901",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Subscription",
            "label": "Subscription",
            "type": 6,
            "isRequired": true,
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::1"
              ],
              "includeAll": false
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "c3d4e5f6-a7b8-9012-cdef-123456789012",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Workspace",
            "label": "Log Analytics Workspace",
            "type": 5,
            "isRequired": true,
            "query": "resources\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces'\n| project id",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "{Subscription}"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::1"
              ],
              "resourceTypeFilter": {
                "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces": true
              }
            },
            "queryType": 1
          },
          {
            "id": "d4e5f6a7-b8c9-0123-defa-234567890123",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "AnalyticsCostPerGB",
            "label": "Analytics Tier Cost/GB ($)",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": "5.55"
          },
          {
            "id": "e5f6a7b8-c9d0-1234-efab-345678901234",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "AuxiliaryCostPerGB",
            "label": "Auxiliary/Data Lake Tier Cost/GB ($)",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": "0.11"
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## Cost Summary"
      },
      "name": "summaryHeader"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "let totalMB = coalesce(toscalar(\n    Usage\n    | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n    | where IsBillable == true\n    | summarize sum(Quantity)\n), 0.0);\nlet totalGB = round(totalMB / 1024, 2);\nlet analyticsCost = round(totalGB * {AnalyticsCostPerGB}, 2);\nlet auxiliaryCost = round(totalGB * {AuxiliaryCostPerGB}, 2);\nlet savings = round(analyticsCost - auxiliaryCost, 2);\ndatatable(Metric:string, Value:real)\n[\n    'Total Billable Ingestion (GB)', totalGB,\n    'Est. Cost at Analytics Tier ($)', analyticsCost,\n    'Est. Cost at Auxiliary Tier ($)', auxiliaryCost,\n    'Potential Savings ($)', savings\n]",
        "size": 4,
        "title": "Ingestion Cost Estimates for Selected Period",
        "noDataMessage": "No ingestion data found",
        "timeContext": {
          "durationMs": 0
        },
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {
            "columnMatch": "Metric",
            "formatter": 1
          },
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "Value",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "auto"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "minimumFractionDigits": 2,
                "maximumFractionDigits": 2
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "name": "costSummaryTiles"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "---\n## Table Retention Plans\nShows the configured retention plan for each table in the selected workspace. Tables on the **Analytics** plan incur standard ingestion and query costs. Tables on the **Auxiliary** (Data Lake) plan have significantly lower ingestion costs but limited query capabilities."
      },
      "name": "tablePlansHeader"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "resources\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces/tables'\n| where id startswith '{Workspace}'\n| extend Plan = tostring(properties.plan)\n| extend RetentionInDays = toint(properties.retentionInDays)\n| extend TotalRetentionInDays = toint(properties.totalRetentionInDays)\n| project ['Table Name']=name, Plan, ['Interactive Retention (Days)']=RetentionInDays, ['Total Retention (Days)']=TotalRetentionInDays\n| sort by Plan asc, ['Table Name'] asc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Table Plans & Retention Configuration",
        "noDataMessage": "No tables found for the selected workspace",
        "queryType": 1,
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Subscription}"
        ],
        "visualization": "table",
        "gridSettings": {
          "formatters": [
            {
              "columnMatch": "Plan",
              "formatter": 18,
              "formatOptions": {
                "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                "thresholdsGrid": [
                  {
                    "operator": "==",
                    "thresholdValue": "Analytics",
                    "representation": "success",
                    "text": "{0}{1}"
                  },
                  {
                    "operator": "==",
                    "thresholdValue": "Auxiliary",
                    "representation": "2",
                    "text": "{0}{1}"
                  },
                  {
                    "operator": "==",
                    "thresholdValue": "Basic",
                    "representation": "warning",
                    "text": "{0}{1}"
                  },
                  {
                    "operator": "Default",
                    "thresholdValue": null,
                    "representation": "unknown",
                    "text": "{0}{1}"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "filter": true,
          "sortBy": [
            {
              "itemKey": "Plan",
              "sortOrder": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "tablePlansQuery"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "---\n## Data Ingestion by Table\nDisplays billable data ingested (in GB) per table over the selected time range, with estimated costs calculated at both the Analytics and Auxiliary tier rates."
      },
      "name": "ingestionHeader"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "Usage\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where IsBillable == true\n| summarize IngestedMB = sum(Quantity) by DataType\n| extend ['Ingested (GB)'] = round(IngestedMB / 1024, 2)\n| extend ['Est. Analytics Cost ($)'] = round(['Ingested (GB)'] * {AnalyticsCostPerGB}, 2)\n| extend ['Est. Auxiliary Cost ($)'] = round(['Ingested (GB)'] * {AuxiliaryCostPerGB}, 2)\n| project ['Table Name']=DataType, ['Ingested (GB)'], ['Est. Analytics Cost ($)'], ['Est. Auxiliary Cost ($)']\n| sort by ['Ingested (GB)'] desc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Billable Ingestion by Table",
        "noDataMessage": "No ingestion data found for the selected time range",
        "timeContext": {
          "durationMs": 0
        },
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "table",
        "gridSettings": {
          "formatters": [
            {
              "columnMatch": "Ingested \\(GB\\)",
              "formatter": 4,
              "formatOptions": {
                "palette": "blue"
              },
              "numberFormat": {
                "unit": 0,
                "options": {
                  "style": "decimal",
                  "minimumFractionDigits": 2,
                  "maximumFractionDigits": 2
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "columnMatch": "Est. Analytics Cost",
              "formatter": 0,
              "numberFormat": {
                "unit": 0,
                "options": {
                  "style": "decimal",
                  "minimumFractionDigits": 2,
                  "maximumFractionDigits": 2
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "columnMatch": "Est. Auxiliary Cost",
              "formatter": 0,
              "numberFormat": {
                "unit": 0,
                "options": {
                  "style": "decimal",
                  "minimumFractionDigits": 2,
                  "maximumFractionDigits": 2
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "filter": true,
          "sortBy": [
            {
              "itemKey": "Ingested (GB)",
              "sortOrder": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "ingestionQuery"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "Usage\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where IsBillable == true\n| summarize IngestedMB = sum(Quantity) by DataType\n| extend IngestedGB = round(IngestedMB / 1024, 2)\n| top 15 by IngestedGB desc\n| project DataType, IngestedGB",
        "size": 1,
        "title": "Top 15 Tables by Ingestion Volume (GB)",
        "timeContext": {
          "durationMs": 0
        },
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "barchart",
        "chartSettings": {
          "xAxis": "DataType",
          "yAxis": [
            "IngestedGB"
          ],
          "showLegend": true
        }
      },
      "name": "ingestionBarChart"
    }
  ],
  "fallbackResourceIds": [],
  "styleSettings": {},
  "$schema": "https://github.com/Microsoft/Application-Insights-Workbooks/blob/master/schema/workbook.json"
}
